data.description: Discover the perfect blend of comfort and charm in this 3-bed, 2-bath haven with 1566 sq/ft of living space tucked away in a peaceful cul-de-sac. Thoughtfully designed, the open-concept layout seamlessly connects the living, dining, and kitchen areas. The master suite offers a private retreat and large walk-in closet, while the backyard oasis invites outdoor relaxation. With modern amenities including stainless steel appliances, detailed trimwork and a two-car garage, this home promises convenience. Located near East Limestone High, Madison, and Athens communities, it's not just a home; it's a lifestyle.
